cs.CR, cs.SE, cs.PL, cs.SI, cs.DC 

This paper focuses on analyzing the security of web communication in mobile apps, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also involves developing a tool to statically identify web API URLs, which could fall under software engineering (cs.SE) and programming languages (cs.PL). The analysis of the commonly-used communication libraries and their usage in apps could also fall under systems and information theory (cs.SI) and distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC).
